Sentencas: The electrochemical performance of LSM-Pd composite material as current collector of SOFC cathode is studied on (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.9)MnO3 (LSM90) cathode.
Titulo: Performance of a novel La(Sr)MnO3-Pd composite current collector for solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The influence of Pd content on contact resistance is investigated.
Titulo: Performance of a novel La(Sr)MnO3-Pd composite current collector for solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The investigation shows that the contact resistance of LSM-Pd is about 20 m Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C when the composite contains 8 wt% Pd, and it could be comparable to pure Pt.
Titulo: Performance of a novel La(Sr)MnO3-Pd composite current collector for solid oxide fuel cell cathode

Sentencas: The ohmic resistance of a single cell using LSM-Pd composite is about 255 m Omega cm(2) that contains 4 wt% Pd as current collector, this value is close to that of a cell using expensive Pt paste as current collector.
Titulo: Performance of a novel La(Sr)MnO3-Pd composite current collector for solid oxide fuel cell cathode
